    "name": "section-consultation",
    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-gradient-brand text-ivory\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24\"><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center\"><h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-heading font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-medium leading-[1.1] mb-8\">Request your <span class=\"text-accent\">Free Consultation</span> today.</h2><p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-subtext text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 font-sans text-[#1a4a6e]\">Take the first step toward the smile you deserve. Our complimentary consultation includes a full exam, advanced imaging, and a personalized treatment plan tailored to your goals. No pressure, no obligation - just honest answers from a team that genuinely cares.</p><div class=\"space-y-6 mb-12\"><div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-benefit-1 flex items-center gap-5\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-primary-subtle\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-primary\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-benefit-1-title font-bold text-xl font-serif\">Comprehensive Exam</h4><p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-benefit-1-description text-sm mt-1 font-sans text-[#1a4a6e]\">Full oral health assessment by our experienced team.</p></div></div><div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-benefit-2 flex items-center gap-5\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-primary-subtle\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-primary\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-benefit-2-title font-bold text-xl font-serif\">Digital Imaging</h4><p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-benefit-2-description text-sm mt-1 font-sans text-[#1a4a6e]\">State-of-the-art digital imaging for precise diagnostics.</p></div></div><div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-benefit-3 flex items-center gap-5\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-primary-subtle\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-primary\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-benefit-3-title font-bold text-xl font-serif\">Custom Treatment Plan</h4><p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-benefit-3-description text-sm mt-1 font-sans text-[#1a4a6e]\">A roadmap designed around your goals and timeline.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"bg-white p-6 md:p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-100 relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-form-heading font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium mb-8 text-center text-white\">Request Your Consultation</h3><form class=\"space-y-5\" data-form-submit=\"\" data-form-name=\"Consultation Request\" data-project-id=\"{{form_project_id}}\"><div class=\"hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><input type=\"text\" name=\"website\" tabindex=\"-1\" autocomplete=\"off\"></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5\"><div><label class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-form-label-name block text-xs font-bold text-white/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 ml-1 font-sans\">Full Name</label><input type=\"text\" name=\"Full Name\" data-label=\"Full Name\" required class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-form-input-name w-full p-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:bg-white focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none font-sans\" placeholder=\"John Doe\" /></div><div><label class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-form-label-phone block text-xs font-bold text-white/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 ml-1 font-sans\">Phone Number</label><input type=\"tel\" name=\"Phone Number\" data-label=\"Phone Number\" required class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-form-input-phone w-full p-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:bg-white focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none font-sans\" placeholder=\"(555) 123-4567\" /></div></div><div><label class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-form-label-email block text-xs font-bold text-white/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 ml-1 font-sans\">Email Address</label><input type=\"email\" name=\"Email Address\" data-label=\"Email Address\" required class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-form-input-email w-full p-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:bg-white focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none font-sans\" placeholder=\"john@example.com\" /></div><div><label class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-consultation-component-form-label-message block text-xs font-bold text-white/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 ml-1 font-sans\">Message